                                "en": "In a moment of <w>frankness</w> he told me about his difficult childhood."
                            }
                        },
                        {
                            "text": "Я не был готов к таким личным <w>откровениям</w> от малознакомого человека.",
                            "target_lang_translations": {
                                "en": "I was not ready for such personal <w>confessions</w> from a person I barely knew."
                            }
